dc_title_s: Carte et description generale de Dauphiné: avec les confins des pais Provinces voisines; le tout Racourcy et reduict par Jean de Beins ingenieur et geographe du roi.; Carte et description generale de Davphine
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. Dedication to the king in the bottom right corner. Includes the Savoy and Dauphine coat of arms. From the Composite Atlas of France, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 36 x 48 cm.
